## Prerequisites
- Linux or macOS
- Python 3
- CPU or NVIDIA GPU + CUDA CuDNN

## Setting enviroments(Installation)

-创建环境： conda create --name FA_generation python=3.6
-激活环境： conda activate FA_generation
-依赖库安装： pip install -r requirements.txt


### 1. Train/Test (Resnet + L1 loss)

- Train the model :
```
python train.py --dataroot ./datasets/FFA --name FFA_res_l1 --model pix2pix --netG resnet_9blocks

```

- Test the model:
```
python test.py --dataroot ./datasets/FFA --name FFA_res_l1 --model pix2pix --netG resnet_9blocks

```

### 2. Train/Test (Resnet + L1 loss + perceptual loss)

- Train the model :
```
python train.py --dataroot ./datasets/FFA --name FFA_res_l1_lp --model pix2pixlp --netG resnet_9blocks

```

- Test the model:
```
python test.py --dataroot ./datasets/FFA --name FFA_res_l1_lp --model pix2pixlp --netG resnet_9blocks

```

### 3. Train/Test (Resnet + L1 loss + perceptual loss + local saliency loss)(Final Model!!!)

- Train the model :
```
python train.py --dataroot ./datasets --name FFA_res_lp_lsal --model pix2pixlsal --netG resattgen --netD SD --preprocess none

```

- Test the model:
```
python test.py --dataroot ./datasets/FFA --name FFA_res_lp_lsal --model pix2pixlsal --netG resnet_9blocks

```








